[DQC.US.0041.73] The dimension default defined for the axis in the US GAAP Taxonomy should not be changed in a company extension taxonomy. The default for the us-gaap:RelatedPartyTransactionsByRelatedPartyAxis in the base taxonomy is us-gaap:RelatedPartyDomain, but the default has been replaced with us-gaap:RelatedPartyTransactionDomain in the extension taxonomy role 156 - Disclosure - RELATED PARTY TRANSACTIONS (Narrative) (Details). This issue is addressed in Question E.16 (Updated 02/05/2013) (formerly Question 38) of the SEC Staff Interpretations and FAQs Related to Interactive Data Disclosure. Rule version: 9.0.0RC1 -
